@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@apiKey = test
@logicalBucket = images
@objectKey = sample-avatar.png

### 1) Bật public link cho logical bucket
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/api/public-buckets
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "bucket": "{{logicalBucket}}",
  "enabled": true
}

### 2) Upload image (bucket backend vẫn private)
# Sau request này lấy header `x-s3proxy-direct-url`, ví dụ:
# http://localhost:3000/public/AbCdEf...
PUT {{baseUrl}}/{{logicalBucket}}/{{objectKey}}
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: image/png

< ./sample-avatar.png

### 3) Tải file qua public URL do proxy sinh (không cần x-api-key)
# Dán URL thực tế từ x-s3proxy-direct-url vào đây.
GET http://localhost:3000/public/REPLACE_WITH_TOKEN

### 4) List cấu hình public buckets
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/api/public-buckets
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### 5) (Tuỳ chọn) Tắt public link cho bucket
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/api/public-buckets
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "bucket": "{{logicalBucket}}",
  "enabled": false
}
